<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Burkhard von Mengersreuth</head><p>Der Rat versichert Freundschaft wegen des Überfalls zwischen Hof und Plauen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_246" id="123r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_246_r1l1"><expan>Burkarte<ex>n</ex></expan> von menigoſreẅt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_246_r1l4"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Burkhart als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / wıe eẅch geſagt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_246_r1l3">ſey </ab></add> daʒ wır eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r1l5">ın ſchulden <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . Jr ſüllt bey der nom <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſeın dıe <expan>etlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r1l6"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> nehſt <expan>geſcheh<ex>en</ex></expan> ıſt <expan>ʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> dem hof vnd plawen etc . das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r1l7">wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıe dıe ſache antrıft kein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r1l8">klag noch rede gehört . daʒ ſıe eẅch <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> in <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dechtnuſſ</expan> gehabt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r1l9"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . Alſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır eẅch der ſache verwıſſen vnd eẅch hinfür </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_246_r1l10">keins argen <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> gewarten . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_246" id="123r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Burkarte<ex>n</ex></expan> von Menigosrewt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Burkhart, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ewch gesagt
                            <add>sey</add>, daz wir ewch in schulden <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                        ir süllt bey der nom <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> sein, die
                                <expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        nehst <expan>gescheh<ex>en</ex></expan> ist <expan>zwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        dem Hof und Plawen, etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        von den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, die die sache antrift, kein klag
                        noch rede gehört, daz sie ewch <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> in
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dechtnuss</expan> gehabt
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, also <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        ewch der sache verwissen und ewch hinfür keins argen
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> gewarten. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
                        ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
